### Get all users
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user
Accept: application/json

### Get a specific restaurant's menu
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user/id/5

### Get a specific user by name
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user/name/Diana

### Create a new menu item
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Benjamin",
  "surname1": "Oropecha",
  "surname2": "Acosta",
  "email": "miss.bro@why.net",
  "password": "1234",
  "phoneNumber": "1209038475",
  "userType": "CUSTOMER"
}

### Update an existing user
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/user/id/7
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Anthony",
  "surname1": "Mora",
  "surname2": "Acosta",
  "email": "miss.bro@mind.mx",
  "password": "1812",
  "phoneNumber": "5518343724",
  "userType": "RESTAURANT_OWNER",
  "rate":5
}

### Delete a user by ID
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/user/id/2
Content-Type: application/json


### Authenticate a user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/auth
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "miss.bro@why.net",
  "password": "1234"
}